channel.title: Solve the color Coded picture and get a cookie!
channel.description:
Please download the attachment to see the picture better!
Hello, I can't get my server to work, I have searched around and corrected various things according to guides and tutorials here on the website, but I still can't get it to work. Please help. Below is a picture! I've tried many things, different compilers, etc.
You might see the picture best if you download the picture I attached. ________________ [img]http://i216.photobucket.com/albums/cc48/vthokie4me/help-1.jpg[/img]
Heres what the colors mean starting with number 1 (the light green one) of the color coded boxes at the bottom:
1. Runserver.bat 2. System Properties - Environment Variables 3. Java Folder 4. Linksys ROUTER 5. Me talking to my friend trying to join server 6. Router IP Address 7. My Modem Information 8. Ipconfig 9. No-IP
And my no-ip pic is there but I accidently made it orange.
